      "text": "9. Un dewe tohs teem Gibeo- nitereem Rohſa/ un tee pakahre tohs us to Kalnu preeſch ta KUNGA. Un tee feptizi gabje kohva bohjâ/ un nomirre plau- jama Laika Eefahkumâ/ kad to Meeschu Ptaufchana fahkahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tad nehme Rizpa/ Ajus Metta weenu Maifin/ un isplat- tija to us to Akmini Ptaufcha- nas Gefahkumâ/ teekans Uhdens no Debbesim us teem pileja/ un ta ne liike tohs Putmus appakſch Debbes us tecni nahkt Deena/ nedz tohsLauka Swehrus Nakti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un Dahwidam tappe fhah- fihts/ ko Rizpa Ajus Metta/ Saula leeke Seewa bij darrijfi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Un Dahwids nogahje/ un nehme Saula/ un winna Dehla Jonataua Kaulus no teem Nam- neekeem no Jabefa eekſch Gilea- das/ kas tohs bij ſagguscht no Betsana Eelas/ fur tee Wiliste- ri tohs bij pakahruschi/ tad Dee- nâ/ kad tee Wilisteri Saulu Gil- boa kawe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un usnetfe vo tenneees Saula Kaulus/ un Jonatana wixxa Dehla Kaulus/ un fafrab- je tohs ar to Pakahrtu Kanleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un aprakke Saula un winna Dehla Jonatana Kaulus\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "eeſch Benjamin Semunes/ eeſch Zeelas/ Riſa tawa Tehwa Rappâ/ un tee Darrija wiſu/ ko tas Rehniasch bij pawehlejs. Ta tappeDeews pehz schim tai Sem- mei falihdsinahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Pehz btja atkak Karſch ſtarp teem Wilistereem un Isra- elu. Un Dahwids nogahje un winna Kalpt ar winnu/ un kar- roja prett teem Wilistereem. Un Dahwids apgurre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Un Jesbus no Nobas weens no Rawus Behrneem/ kam weens Schkehps btja trihs ſunts Warra Sihketus Simag- gunâ/ un wiꞥſch bija apjohts ar janmu Sobbinu/ tas dohina- ja Dahwidu kaut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Bet Abisajus/ Zerujas Dehls palihdſeja tam/ un lawe to Wilisteri/ ka tas nomirre. Tad swehreja Dahwida Wihti tam/ un fazzija: Tew ne buhs wairs ar mums eet Karrâ/ ka tu to Gaischumu. eekſch Israeta ne iſdſeffi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Pehz bija atkak Karſch Nobâ prett teem Wilistereem. Tad kawe Sivekajus tas Usatite- ris Satu! kas no Rawus Behrneem bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Wehl bija atkak Karſch Sobâ prett teem Wilistereem/ tad kawe Elanans Jaere Oregi- ma Dehls Betlaemiteris/ Goli- ata ta Getitexa (Brathli) kant tasSchkehps bija ka weena Weh- wera Reestawa.\n"
    },
    {
